The paper deals with video captioning, which is a task in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new model that uses deep learning techniques, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The proposed model also involves memory operations, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
